    "Yaghoubi et al. [7] developed a PETA dataset with 19,000 pictures depicting 8,705 pedestrians.",
    "In addition, they included 61 binary attributes and four multi-category variables for each wayfarer.",
    "A dataset named aPY was created by Ashrafi,Shokouhi,and Ayatollahi [8] by tagging 12,679 specimens of Pascal VOC.",
    "Every test in this dataset is given a 64dimensional attribute description.",
    "In their study, the authors in reference [9] provided a comprehensive analysis of 204-D ascribe angles for 29 different kinds of tests in the COCO dataset."
